<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>A futile attempt at forgiveness, I know.</p>
<p>&quot;As always.&quot;</p>
<p>You'd always say.</p>
<p>And I get that, I really do.</p>
<p>But now I realize, I wasn't myself anymore.</p>
<p><strong>So this is for you, Ten.</strong></p>
<p>Sorry,</p>
<p>And goodbye.</p>
